title: ‘Euphoria’ Season 2, Episode 4 Recap featuring Eric Dane
description:
Joanna and Nora are back to recap the explosive episode of 'Euphoria' and all of the drama with Cal that unfolds (11:19). Later, Joanna sits down with actor Eric Dane to discuss the evolution of his character Cal and where this episode leaves him (50:34).
Hosts: Joanna Robinson and Nora Princiotti
Guest: Eric Dane
Producer: Steve Ahlman
